body:
Hello~This is Andersen.The following paragraphs seem to be a part of the web's brief introduction,
but I would like to add my feel to the page:
It's my pleasure to build my first web program,
and I wish that with the accumulation of my knowledge and experience,
these pages will be decorated much better than ever before.
![Digimon](http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/64d8bf94gw1e772gb6gg3j20hi5eg7wi.jpg)
                                                          Andersen
                                                        Mar.9th 2016
